The kindergarten is part, too, offices have understood the architects.
The administrative building Avriopoint of Brno is the new headquarters of the company Arch. design.
No one could have expected that also houses a mini nursery school with everything - the walls of colours, imaginative furniture, toys and finally a miniature playground on the terrace.
Since October last year, can make children of employees of Arch. design.
The society of projets-architectonique Arch. design. including the workshops have produced a large number of construction in Brno, has imagined his mini nursery school of business since the first drafts of the building Avriopoint.
It employs about 90 people, especially the age to make children and it was important that women architects and project leaders can quickly return to work.
At the same time as employment contracts in time declined, nursery school is a proposed bonuses to its employees by society Arch. design. as part of its social agenda.
Builders and architects have the opportunity to combine a job taking with the care for the children.
It is the employees of Arch.Design.eux-mêmes who have imagined this nursery school and with the support of the direction they were able to obtain a grant from the European Union and the Ministry of Labour and Social Affairs.
The mini nursery school is funded by the means the European Social Fund through the operational program of Human Resources and State Budget of the Czech Republic.
Thanks to funding allocations (up to 2.8 mil.de CZK). they were able to buy equipment and appliances and after two years to ensure qualified staff and the start.
After the use of the allocation of funding (two years) the company Arch. design. has an obligation after 3 years to operate the mini nursery school on its own funds.
The preparation of the project lasted a year and it is society Economy nominale who has helped to make the request of staffing.
The children's care is provided by a qualified staff, all day a nurse and a kindergarten teacher caring children. children can go to nursery school without age limit, but they have more than three anspour most.
As it is a "mini nursery school" there can only be 5 children present at the same time, but during the day there are more who will replace.
The functioning of the school is responsive to the needs of parents and children of all employees have the same right to use this school without looking at the hierarchical position.
Although agise of a care and individual education, the programme of the mini nursery school is comparable to that for pre-school education.
Children are no that play, but a quality education is also assured - from the beginning to the prep school to teach English.
The class is equipped not only of toys and games imaginative but also a computer that children can use.
The presence of small children in society creates an environment friendly and positive.
Parents can at any time controlling their child and not have the stress of a delay to pick up children in a school far from the workplace of parents.
Parents use their time to work on the most productive way.
It is not surprising that creates a natural relationship of loyalty between employer and employee.
Arch.Design.s' is listed among the companies that offer a bonus of choice for recruiting new employees, and who are friendly to the family and through this program reinforces the HR marketing.
The house still fascinates bones after 100 years. take a look in the interiors of Gaudf.
The roof looks like the back of a saurien, the staircase to a dinosaur spine and the balconies to fish Gules.
Thus is the house Casa Battlo in Barcelona from the architect Antoni Gaudi.
Because of its organic forms, the house has received from the local nickname of Maison bone.
Organic shapes, colours, unusual use of stones, fragments of tiles and mosaîque, housefront recalling the scales and around these curves, this is everything ypique for the Art Nouveau of Antoni Gaudi.
The front facade of the house held its lines of dream, its colours and textures pleasant reminiscent of the nature and animals.
In a more detailed comment is the geometry, pace and order thought with precision.
On the night the facade of the house becomes even more dramatic and is lit so that the impression of brilliance of colours is strengthened.
Leafroll and the twist of the forms also appears in the interiors with the same extent.
The copy in waves the wood window frames, balustrades, the elements of the doors, the oeilleton and lamellae.
The Battlo house that sits in the Eixample district in the market Street Passeig de Gracia to number 43, was born of the construction of a house in 1877 by the architect Emilio Sala Cortes.
The reconstruction has made for two years and the house completed in 1906.
The investor, Joseph Battlo, a wealthy entrepreneur, was first insisted on the demolition of the vieile construction and the construction of another any new but quickly accepted the idea of a reconstruction Gaudf unusual and cheaper.
But the idea of Casa Battlo as home to multiple units was not thought by Gaudi alone.
The Architect Josep Maria Jujol worked with him.
It is precisely on his project that are born decorations for an apartment of representation of the owner of the building and the use of the mosaîque to the facade.
The housefront also worked for other artists and creators.
The plans for the joint work of the house, Casa Battlo began with a believe cooperation between Jujol and Gaudf.
Jujol participated in the construction of the house of Gaudf Casa Mila and the Park Guell in which there are other works of Gaudf.
Locals have nicknamed the hot house just after finishing his because of its organic forms the bone "bone."
Others, with regard to the specific mechanism of opening windows were known as "the house that drink".
It said that at the top of the building there is a sword similar to that of Saint Georges the boss of Catalonia.
Other elements of sculpture of the construction contain hidden.
Gaudf a thought for the house a single system in his time, with central heating vents and chimneys typical.
Their angle of 45 degrees seems odd.
During the establishment Gaudf did not comply with the guidelines of construction and has not been hampered by them.
At the beginning of the building he received on the part of the city the building permits, knowing, of course that the data reported on the reconstruction plans were so vague that during the two years after finishing the City Council was horrified and asked for changes.
It wasn't happy, for example, to members of the city council that the pillars of the construction empiettent public on the sidewalk.
There was never any change, but, on the contrary, only 15 days after the appeal of the city Josep Battlo asked (and satisfaction) got approval to rent the top two floors.
The Owner moved to lower floors.
In the gallery on the second floor there was a common lounge and the third a bedroom and a private part of the apartment.
The ground floor was leased to a jewellery store.
The full house of six floors is shared by a staircase by which you climb up to a roof terrace independent.
All right angles and straight lines were cancelled by the basic elements of reconstruction and their replacement by walls curves.
Gaudi also worked the modern concept of the bond spaces.
The party may be related completely by opening the doors of high society and salons can communicate comfortably or to limit the private space for interviews, more intimate.
The house with the reconstruction of Gaudf received a new addition housefronts toîture nontrad 2-storey and in more.
The Gaudf game with the light is also impressive, blue and white glazed tiles, which is decorated with the inner courtyard and with the wells of lights.
The game in two colours give a maximum of light in all the floors of the house.
It was enough simply to bet on the principle that the white reflête more than the dark who instead absorbs the sun's rays.
The house Casa Battlo which was included in the 2005 World Heritage Fund UNESCO perhaps visited by everyone.
On the first floor of the house is the apartment the more spacious and the splendid more accessible to the public.
The owners have decided to take this step in 2002 to mark the 150th anniversary of the birth of the famous creator.
They continued the visits because they have found that it is a lucrative business and they have broadened the scope of visits to common spaces and the attic including the roof terraces.
The ticket in the monument is not really expensive and costs €16.50; students, pensioners, the groups and the tourist card holders have 20 per cent discount.
The sum is still above the price of entry into the other buildings in the city of Gaudf.
If you want to feel the real atmosphere of the house with its fantastic turrets, you have to quickly find a comrade among residents of the building and visit the house.
How to choose a mattress and a bedspring: women have other criteria than men.
No conspicuous framework, but the quality of the surface reserved at bedtime, so the mattress and the bedspring give a real basis for a good bed.
They must naturally complement harmoniously to appeal to a specific user.
During the election, several things are crucial: the weight, size, age, health status, and sex of the owner.
The type of interior in which it will place the mattress and the bedspring is also important.
A a typical example?
For example, in the cottage where we do not continuously dort latex mattresses are not appropriate because they "warming" gently.
They have, moreover, a weight above the polyurethane mattress 59-65.
It is necessary to return them frequently.
If they do not have enough ventilation ducts in the heart and if they are, in addition, on a strong board, they retain moisture. mold can also be formed.
The habit is also decisive in the election.
That is the clear time abroad, where it often uses mattresses very thick with a layer rammollissante, feels hardly feel well on a low, hard surface.
"It is as well that all hokeyistes returning from NHL complain that they cannot sleep there".
"To their shoulders, legs and ribs, they needed mattress with a layer of foam rammollisante lazy".
"Such mattresses are also recommended for people with diabetes who have a nervous system disorder therefore assume evil" information "joints and the skin," says Sylva Adamczikova who specializes in upholstered furniture.
That is why a few years ago the foam mattress with lazy conquered the hokeyistes and other clients.
"Today everything is working well, Tempur, Italian Magnifex but Czech Tropico have, for example, appropriate mattresses.
You do not need to be a gars of NHL to assess a foam lazy.
The "miracle" just works.
It optimalise its rigidity and its form under the heat absorbed or adapt to the heat of your body.
There is pressure on you and you do not back in the game after a difficult match.
You just sleep better.
The foam lazy also functions as a protection against the esquarres.
For the choice of mattress, depending on your size, add the length of feet, or about 21 / 34 cm.
A man and a woman a size of 180cm have therefore need a bed of 210 / 220 cm.
The minimum width for each for a bed to two places should be 90 cm in total 180 cm.
For beds in a single place, the singles for example, it is recommended to take at least 120 / 140 cm.
It is convenient to visit.
"However, it is a simple rule for the width of the bed: when you are lying on their backs you should ask the hands comfortably with elbows slightly bent. Helena Prokopova, President of the Association of Bourreliers-matelassiers and decorators who has spent several years on the issue of a healthy sleep and ergonomics furniture and Enseign in special schools.
For a bed to two seats each needs its own bedspring and mattresses, so attention during the achât to choose the height of the mattress.
Otherwise you will remain to mount the bedspring at different heights and this is not feasible on all the bed.
The foam mattress should have a minimum height of 14 cm, the mattress springs at least 15 cm, this count for the layer of form and venting at least three centimetres.
"To touch or sitting on the mattress you should not feel the springs," warns Héléna Prokopova.
Each type request a mattresses type of mattress support.
The lit-sommier, when the mattress and the bedspring are united as sisters siamoises, has nothing to do in the bedrooms.
The mattress has aèrent very badly; it should not wash, which is commonly auhourd' today.
And since during the night you perspire normally 0.2. 0.75 l sweat it is clear that after 5 / 7 years, the mattress is beginning to remind a large (and clogged round-holed).
To this specialists refuse to make the claims on a lifetime of 25 years for a mattress or a guarantee for life.
But his but.
And for this a board of experience on the part of sellers: for a mattress 120 / 140cm, give up, for the mattress cover, hygiene or washing but add rather a mattress of protection that vouspouvez easily withdraw and wash.
And even if nowadays it is common to manufacture coatings with zipper for the whole thing, it is to say that after the opening it was two parties (for washing and the size of the washing machine that is very important!) if not manipulation for the larger models (and for a single person) becomes when removes a fight between a light weight and a lorry on a ring.
You have in your bed a rigid instead of a collapsed?
Never!
The maximum for visitors for a bed for a single night.
However equip the board (if there are no vents) and use the mattress springs with a minimum height with springs 15cm bags (Germany) and a layer of Taschenfederken bioventing.
A polyurethane mattress should not be part of a bed of this type.
For the lamellae box to unique position with 14 / 18 lamellae, the so-called latex mattresses or sandwiches (perhaps the combination of latex and coconut), are the ideal but this will always be better for you to have a mattress with more lamellae, 28 and above, where the lamellae are doubled in the bottom half of the kidneys and that it is possible to regulate the rigidity.
For mattresses at several positions it should not take mattress springs because it does not meet the change of position.
Next to the setting of the rigidity of lamellae can also install what is known as a cradle of shoulder.
It is a special liaison lamellae that can put pressure or even tilt the coverslip for Dungeness the shoulder "fit" well.
For men who have the "broadest shoulders back," this is really important.
This thing is already being considered by the mattress manufacturers for the "male" began to use a zone rammollissante across the shoulders.
But they also believe women - they offer a softer surface again at the hips.
