The pressure is spreading in more points and diinue tension.
But of course, attention, as soon as you use a bad pillow (large and inflated air) on good mattress and sleeping, the "more" disappears.
The basic rule is a pillow simple: the pillow must support the head and its spines should reach only the shoulders, so that the shoulder muscles can rest.
Size is the size recommended that the Scandinavians by exmple prefer.
When you are lying on the side, the pillow needs to upgrade (with the cradle of shoulder or the rammollie deck area in the mattress) the shoulders.
