Today, many companies do not hesitate to go to the body to body in competition to find the best brains and engage, as Volkswagen, in a multifaceted cooperation with universities.
Their mission: to recruit the brightest graduates as much as possible in the halls before they enter the labour market and they are courted by others.
And since universities do not publish statements about the performance of their students, trying to identify the exceptional talent in the projects of the practices and loyalty.
