"Some of them are on the verge of complete their studies and soon wish to send their requests for our business". "he says.
Outside the Direct amadouement in the campus, small and medium-sized enterprises are quite classic in participating in the trade fairs where they are engaged in the hunt for brains.
"We are trying to achieve graduates in participating in the shows."
