He advises his clients to be more authenticity.
And, according to Mr. Kriegler, this means, above all, internal measures.
"The best way for an employer to make attractive is through its own aides," he said.
It is, according to the jargon in the sector, the strategy of internal image, i.e., the creation of the image of the employer within its own workforce.
"The staff are the best Messengers."
When dealing well its employees and that they identify with the company, they alone advertising on their employer to their friends and acquaintances.
