For the first time, the DPP has attracted voters, even with the KMT municipal councils.
The event has unveiled most of the main topics of Taiwanese elections, including trucks and flags to aggressive campaign of mass rally with girls who dansaient minimum required.
A mysterious assassination attempt has also been perpetrated.
